Available Tools: get_lab_results | get_latest_results | get_result_history | download_report
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "patient_id": "string", "test_type": "string", "from_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "results": [{ "test": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "reference_range": "string", "status": "normal|high|low" }] }
---
Question: Get the latest blood glucose reading for patient P-8821.
Call: { "func_call": "get_latest_results", "patient_id": "P-8821", "test_type": "glucose", "from_date": "" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "Fasting Glucose", "value": 104, "unit": "mg/dL", "reference_range": "70-99", "status": "high" }] }

Question: Retrieve the complete history of HbA1c tests for patient P-9932 starting from January 1st, 2023 to check trends.
Call: { "func_call": "get_result_history", "patient_id": "P-9932", "test_type": "HbA1c", "from_date": "2023-01-01" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "HbA1c", "value": 6.1, "unit": "%", "reference_range": "4.0-5.6", "status": "high" }, { "test": "HbA1c", "value": 5.9, "unit": "%", "reference_range": "4.0-5.6", "status": "high" }, { "test": "HbA1c", "value": 5.4, "unit": "%", "reference_range": "4.0-5.6", "status": "normal" }] }

Question: Download the official PDF report for the lipid panel conducted on patient P-1102 last week.
Call: { "func_call": "download_report", "patient_id": "P-1102", "test_type": "lipid_panel", "from_date": "2023-10-15" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "Report Generated", "value": 20231022, "unit": "file_id", "reference_range": "N/A", "status": "normal" }] }

